{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_08_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 ミクは凄いね",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　嘘でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? No way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（……いきなりどうしたんだ？）\n（あっちに誰かいるのか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…What’s gotten into her all of a sudden?）\n（Is there someone over there?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.8220801728,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……あの人は――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That person is――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.226856478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "初音ミク……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hatsune Miku…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.9682850996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirが、ライブツアーのために",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――When LizNoir came to Hokkaido",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.8269928533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "北海道にやってきた時のこと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "for their live tour.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6669926132,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.0869919378
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "それにしても、さっきは驚いたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ I was surprised earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.9936600922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "東京からはるばる北海道まで来たからには\nそりゃ、何か面白いことがないかなって期待してたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we came all the way from Tokyo to Hokkaido‚\nI was hoping for something interesting to happen‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8904928006,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.0405990044
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、街でばったりミクに会うとは思わなかったよ\n期待してた以上の驚きだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but I never expected to run into Miku on the street.\nIt was a bigger surprise than I expected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.3554287354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、葵もミクを知ってたんだな\nミクの動画を観てた感じもなかったし、意外だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ you knew Miku‚ huh‚ Aoi?\nI didn’t think you watched her videos‚ so it was a surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "僕の方こそ、君があんなに驚くとは思わなかったよ\nまぁ、事務所で聴いてたことはないから仕方ないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised that you were so surprised.\nWell‚ I guess it’s understandable since you’ve never heard of her at the office.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.500711894
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "大体ゲーセンで音ゲーをやって覚えたからね\nミクの曲は大人気で、沢山収録されてるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I mostly learned about her from playing rhythm games at the arcade.\nHer songs are very popular‚ so they’re included in a lot of games.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（なるほどな。そう言えば前に）\n（葵に音ゲーを勧めたことがあったっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I see. Come to think of it‚）\n（I recommended a rhythm game to Aoi before.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.1647933404
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "そのミクが僕達のライブに出てくれるって言うんだから\nどこでどう縁が繋がるか、分からないもんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And now Miku says she’ll perform at our live show.\nYou never know how fate will connect you with people.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "縁と言えば……昔、麻奈のマネージャーになる前に\n人気アイドルのライブを観に行ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of fate… a long time ago‚ before I became Mana’s manager‚\nI went to see a popular idol’s live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1374662686,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.6408742666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "……へぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "その人気グループのメンバーとは今こうして話してて\nライブのために一緒に北海道まで来てる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now I’m talking with a member of that popular group‚\nand we even came to Hokkaido together for the live show.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.0666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.9057210047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、縁がどう繋がるかなんて\nその時になってみないと分からないもんだよなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You really never know how fate will play out\nuntil it happens‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "はは、そうかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha‚ maybe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.1210727453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99.3503017266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "君と僕達の縁と同じくらい\nミクとの縁も、長くいいものになることを願うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I hope our bond with Miku\nwill also be long and fruitful‚ just like the bond between you and us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0999989827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkastreet-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkastreet-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.3103016693
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、まずはライブ本番まで頑張らないとね\nミクに恥ずかしいところは見せられないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ we have to do our best for the live performance first.\nWe can’t let Miku see us looking bad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3333323161,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4336.129108899996,
          "startTime": 114.669461425
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.6676838999965,
          "startTime": 115.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4361290454
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4361290454
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.669461425
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（その後、ミーティングの末、リズノワはミクと一緒に）\n（ライブで新曲を披露することになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After that‚ after the meeting‚ LizNoir decided to）\n（perform a new song at the live show with Miku.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.4333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（今、リズノワとミクで一緒に新曲を作ってるはずだけど）\n（打ち合わせはうまく進んでいるだろうか……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They should be working on the new song together right now‚）\n（but I wonder how the meeting is going…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.3333307902,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2966.6692098000167,
          "startTime": 129.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "あれ、{user}君\n午後からライブのスタッフと会議って言ってなかった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}-kun.\nDidn’t you say you had a meeting with the live staff this afternoon?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5132587592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_08_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、俺の方はどうにか終わったよ\nそっちは……新曲の進捗はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I somehow managed to finish mine.\nHow about you…? How’s the new song coming along?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.9640708445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.4153189818
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
