      "text": "作詞作曲はミクを中心に進めてるし……\nああ、さっきまでミクとダンス対決をしてたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku is taking the lead on the songwriting and composition…\nOh‚ we were having a dance battle with Miku until just now.",
