      "text": "なるほど、建設的な対決で良かったよ\n……それで、どうだったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ it’s good that it was a constructive battle.\n…So‚ how did it go?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.8000269573,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
